        <p> Then I took care of my dirty wash. It's easy here. On the ground floor there is a laundromat that even offered small money for small money carefree service. I only gave a lady there my bags with my clothes, my room number and paid. In the evening I got my clothes back dry and merged. Almost like before at Mutti at home, only that I can pay about 2.50 euros for it today. </p>
        <p>
            <strong> Thank you mom for spoiling me in the past. </strong>
        </p>
        <p> Today I wanted to visit another area of &#8203;&#8203;the city in which I have not yet been. So I got two bottles of water and made my way. The route was less than 3 km long, but the sun burned quite a bit again. I had chosen the Hayahay Treehouse Bar as the goal. From there you have a nice view over the water and you can see 3 neighboring islands. When I arrived at the destination, I had drunk the now warm water and first needed a mango shake and a sprite to cool down again. There I stayed in the shade for a while and enjoyed the view from the tree house.  Unfortunately, I found that I am getting really old. Not even for 1 hour in the sun and I'm ripe for a afternoon sleep? I think I'm getting old !!!! </p>
